This firmware requires two third-party components that are NOT included in
this repository and are fetched by scripts/fetch-components.sh (see FIRMWARE_BUILD.md):
  - ML-KEM-1024 from PQClean (Public Domain / CC0)   github.com/PQClean/PQClean
  - BLAKE3 reference C implementation (CC0-1.0 / Apache-2.0)
                                                     github.com/BLAKE3-team/BLAKE3

The optional Linux debug client (linux-debug/) links against OpenSSL
(Apache-2.0) for its host-side crypto; OpenSSL is a system dependency and is
not included in this repository.
